=== 共和党 ===
共和党的提名程序包括初選和[[黨團會議|黨團會議]]，在全國50個州分、[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]、[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]、[[關島|關島]]、[[美屬維爾京群島|美屬維爾京群島]]、[[美屬薩摩亞|美屬薩摩亞]]和[[北馬里亞納群島|北馬里亞納群島]]舉行。黨團會議先把各黨代表獲分派到所屬州分和全國大會，然後才舉行黨代表選舉。黨代表的選舉辦法每州各異，參選人可以透過當地地方大會、提交提名名單、委員會會議或直接從黨團會議及初選中當選。

==== 初選 ====
在初選前期早早宣布加入角逐共和黨提名的參選人包括眾議員[[榮·保羅|榮·保羅]]、前州長[[蒂姆·普蘭提|蒂姆·普蘭提]]、前州長[[米特·罗姆尼|米特·罗姆尼]]和前眾議院議長[[紐特·金里奇|紐特·金里奇]]。2011年5月11日，第一場辯論在[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]][[格林维尔_(南卡罗来纳州)|格林维尔]]舉行，商人[[赫尔曼·凯恩|赫尔曼·凯恩]]、前州長[[加里·约翰逊|加里·约翰逊]]、保羅、普蘭提、前州長[[里克·桑托勒姆|里克·桑托勒姆]]參與其中。一個月後的另一場辯論參與者大致相同，除了约翰逊缺席外，加入戰團的還有金里奇、罗姆尼、前駐華大使[[洪博培|洪博培]]、眾議員[[米歇爾·巴赫曼|米歇爾·巴赫曼]]。在[[艾奧瓦州|艾奧瓦州]]黨團會議開展前合計有十三場辯論。

在2011年8月13日於艾奧瓦州舉行的[[艾姆斯民意調查|艾姆斯民意調查]]是初選前夕的焦點之一。巴赫曼在民調中以些微優勢勝出<ref>{{Cite news |last=Goldman |first=Russell |url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/politics/2012/01/bachmann-drops-out-of-presidential-race/ |title=Michele Bachmann Drops Out of Presidential Race |publisher=ABC News |date=2012-07-05 |accessdate=2012-11-06 |archive-date=2020-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212011907/https://abcnews.go.com/blogs/politics/2012/01/bachmann-drops-out-of-presidential-race/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而普蘭提和眾議員[[2012年撒迪厄斯·麦科特尔美国总统竞选|撒迪厄斯·麦科特尔]]則因支持度不足宣布退選<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/61098.html |title=Barred hopefuls make debate plans |last=Summers |first=Juana |date=2011-08-11 |work=[[Politico_(newspaper)|Politico]] |accessdate=2012-07-05 |archive-date=2015-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227194024/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/61098.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部分保守派選民認為羅姆尼的政策太[[自由主義|自由]]和溫和，於是一眾被指是「反羅姆尼」的共和黨人便引起關注<ref>{{cite web|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2012/01/09/us-campaign-romney-idINDEE80804P20120109|title=Romney's rivals running out of time to stop him|first=Tim|last=Reid|date=2012-01-09|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2012-07-05|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006184242/http://in.reuters.com/article/2012/01/09/us-campaign-romney-idINDEE80804P20120109|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Norington, Brad [http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/romney-has-money-but-lacks-conviction/story-e6frg6ux-1226285540352 "Romney has money but lacks conviction"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/romney-has-money-but-lacks-conviction/story-e6frg6ux-1226285540352 |date=20120309034435 }}, ''[[The_Australian|The Australian]]''. Retrieved July 12, 2012.</ref>，包括商人[[唐納德·川普|唐納德·川普]]<ref>Cohn, Alicia M. [http://thehill.com/video/campaign/198319-trump-romney-lacks-the-courage-to-participate-in-his-debate "Trump says Romney lacks the 'courage' to participate in Newsmax debate"] {{Wayback|url=http://thehill.com/video/campaign/198319-trump-romney-lacks-the-courage-to-participate-in-his-debate |date=20210111110852 }}, ''[[The_Hill_(newspaper)|The Hill]]''. Retrieved July 12, 2012.</ref>、前州長[[莎拉·佩林|莎拉·佩林]]<ref>Stanley, Timothy (March 30, 2012) [http://www.cnn.com/2012/03/29/opinion/stanley-sarah-palin/ "If only Sarah Palin had run ..."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/03/29/opinion/stanley-sarah-palin/ |date=20200812154816 }}, [[CNN|CNN]]. Retrieved July 12, 2012.</ref>、州長[[里克·佩里|里克·佩里]]<ref>Cohen, Tom; Silverleib, Alan (September 1, 2011) [http://articles.cnn.com/2011-09-01/politics/republican.nomination_1_romney-and-bachmann-tea-party-sarah-palin?_s=PM:POLITICS "Seeking the 'anti-Romney' in the Republican presidential race"] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.cnn.com/2011-09-01/politics/republican.nomination_1_romney-and-bachmann-tea-party-sarah-palin?_s=PM:POLITICS |date=20120712110209 }}, [[CNN|CNN]].com. Retrieved July 12, 2012.</ref>。當中只有佩里正式宣布參選，可是他在辯論中表現欠佳，不足以威脅在競選中領跑的凯恩和金里奇。凯恩卻因醜聞纏身在2011年末退選<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsday.com/news/nation/herman-cain-suspends-presidential-campaign-1.3355834|title=Herman Cain suspends presidential campaign|date=2011-12-03|work=Newsday|accessdate=2012-07-05}}</ref>。只能晉身一場辯論的约翰逊退黨轉投[[自由意志党_(美国)|自由意志黨]]繼續競選<ref>{{cite web |url=http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/12/28/liberated-gary-johnson-seeks-libertarian-nomination/ |title='Liberated' Gary Johnson seeks Libertarian nomination |publisher=CNN |date=2011-12-28 |accessdate=2011-12-28 |author=Stewart, Rebecca |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817125901/https://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/12/28/liberated-gary-johnson-seeks-libertarian-nomination/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年1月，共和黨黨內初選正式開鑼。首三場初選中，桑托勒姆在[[艾奧瓦州|艾奧瓦州]]黨團會議中先拔頭籌，羅姆尼在[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]初選勝出<ref>[http://mobile.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-21/rick-santorum-is-declared-winner-of-iowa-caucuses-by-state-party-leaders Rick Santorum Is Declared Winner of Iowa Caucuses by State Party Leaders"] {{Wayback|url=http://mobile.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-21/rick-santorum-is-declared-winner-of-iowa-caucuses-by-state-party-leaders |date=20121020033130 }} (January 21, 2012). [[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]].</ref>，金里奇出乎意料地以絕對優勢取下[[南卡羅萊納州|南卡羅萊納州]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/01/21/newt-gingrich-s-surprise-win-in-south-carolina-panics-republicans.html |title=Newt Gingrich's Surprise Win in South Carolina Panics Republicans |first=Paul |last=Begala |date=2012-01-21 |accessdate=2012-11-06 |archive-date=2017-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525040254/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/01/21/newt-gingrich-s-surprise-win-in-south-carolina-panics-republicans.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這是共和黨史上首次出現首三場初選由不同候選人勝出的情況<ref name="Newtwins">{{cite web |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Elections/President/2012/0121/Newt-Gingrich-wins-South-Carolina.-Can-he-do-the-same-in-Florida |title=Newt Gingrich wins South Carolina. Can he do the same in Florida? |work=[[Christian_Science_Monitor|Christian Science Monitor]] |date=2012-01-21 |accessdate=2012-07-10 |author=Knickerbocker, Brad |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127031218/https://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Elections/President/2012/0121/Newt-Gingrich-wins-South-Carolina.-Can-he-do-the-same-in-Florida |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在早期初選中失利的候選人紛紛宣布退下火線，先是在艾奧瓦州僅列第五的巴赫曼<ref>Sarah Wheaton, "[http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/04/bachmann-says-she-will-not-continue-in-the-race/ Bachmann Says She Will Not Continue in the Race] {{Wayback|url=http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/04/bachmann-says-she-will-not-continue-in-the-race/ |date=20201118231249 }}" (January 4, 2012). ''The New York Times''.</ref>，然後是在新罕布什尔州得到第三的洪博培，還有在南卡羅萊納州初選開始前宣布退選的佩里<ref>{{Cite news |first1=Jeff |last1=Zeleny |first2=Michael D. |last2=Shear |newspaper=The New York Times |title=Perry to End Bid for Presidency |date=2012-01-19 |url=http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/19/perry-to-end-bid-for-presidency/ |accessdate=2012-07-10 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124133224/https://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/19/perry-to-end-bid-for-presidency/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[超級星期二|超級星期二]]前夕，桑托勒姆在2月7日一口氣贏得三個州<ref>Madison, Lucy (February 8, 2012) [http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-57373308-503544/santorum-hopes-to-build-momentum-from-3-state-sweep/ "Santorum hopes to build momentum from 3-state sweep"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-57373308-503544/santorum-hopes-to-build-momentum-from-3-state-sweep/ |date=20131111210754 }}, [[CBS_News|CBS News]]. Retirieved August 27, 2012</ref>，而羅姆尼則取得[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]在內的餘下七個州的初選。涉及十個州共391張黨代表票的超級星期二在3月6日舉行，結果羅姆尼取下六個州鞏固領先優勢，桑托勒姆共得三個州，而金里奇只贏得家鄉[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]<ref>[http://www.cnn.com/election/2012/primaries/dates/20120306 "Results: March 6, 2012 - Super Tuesday"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/election/2012/primaries/dates/20120306 |date=20200812161118 }}, [[CNN|CNN]]. Retrieved July 12, 2012.</ref>。三月餘下的日子中共有266個代表在12場選舉中投票，包括海外屬地的初選和本屆首個地方大會（懷俄明州各縣大會）。桑托勒姆贏得[[肯薩斯州|肯薩斯州]]和三個南部州分，但已難以追趕在3月所有選舉中贏得過半票數的羅姆尼。

4月10日，桑托勒姆終止競選，使羅姆尼成為唯一具有競爭力的候選人，他的對手中只剩下自稱「最後一個保守派」的金里奇依然未退選<ref>Gabriel, Trip (April 10, 2012) [http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/04/10/gingrich-says-hes-in-the-race-to-the-end/# "Gingrich Says He's in the Race to the End"] {{Wayback|url=http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/04/10/gingrich-says-hes-in-the-race-to-the-end/ |date=20201124185154 }}, ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''.</ref>。未幾，金里奇在4月25日透過發言人宣布將在5月1日退出<ref>[http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2012/04/25/overheard-on-cnn-com-what-brought-down-gingrichs-campaign-whats-next/ "Overheard on CNN.com: What brought down Gingrich's campaign? What's next?"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2012/04/25/overheard-on-cnn-com-what-brought-down-gingrichs-campaign-whats-next/ |date=20201125173849 }}, [[CNN|CNN]]. April 25, 2012.</ref>。在消息公布的同一天，共和黨全國委員會宣布羅姆尼成為預定獲提名人<ref>{{cite news |last=Shear |first=Michael D. |date=2012-04-25 |title=Republican National Committee Backs Romney |url=http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/04/25/republican-national-committee-backs-romney/ |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2012-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126175406/https://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/04/25/republican-national-committee-backs-romney/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保羅從未正式宣布退選，但其競選活動在5月14日已終結。5月29日，[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]初選為羅姆尼錦上添花，此額外的155張代表人票讓他得到獲黨提名的足夠票數<ref name="romneyclinches">Holland, Steve (May 30, 2012) [http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/30/us-usa-campaign-romney-idUSBRE84T02720120530 "Romney clinches Republican 2012 nomination in Texas"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/30/us-usa-campaign-romney-idUSBRE84T02720120530 |date=20150924164249 }}, [[Reuters|Reuters]]. Retrieved May 30, 2012.</ref>。

8月28日共和黨全國大會正式提名羅姆尼為代表該黨的總統候選人<ref name="CBS News nominee">{{cite web | url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-57502088-503544/republican-delegates-nominate-mitt-romney/ | title=Republican delegates nominate Mitt Romney | publisher=CBS News | date=2012-08-28 | accessdate=2012-08-28 | author=Caldwell, Leigh Ann | archive-date=2013-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111210757/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-57502088-503544/republican-delegates-nominate-mitt-romney/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩天後，羅姆尼在同一場合發表接受提名演說<ref>O'Brien, Michael (August 30, 2012) [http://nbcpolitics.nbcnews.com/_news/2012/08/30/13578981-romney-accepts-nomination-says-the-time-has-come-to-turn-the-page?lite "Romney accepts nomination, says 'The time has come to turn the page' "] {{Wayback|url=http://nbcpolitics.nbcnews.com/_news/2012/08/30/13578981-romney-accepts-nomination-says-the-time-has-come-to-turn-the-page?lite |date=20200806223420 }}, [[NBC_News|NBC News]]. Retrieved August 31, 2012.</ref>。

